Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會不會對PKF型號的義體太過自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就過了使用年限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是就算這樣你還是會贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽起來很不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#21  敗逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擊倒切斷痛覺的義體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有震動腦部了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前是游擊隊員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會獲勝大概是因為些微的動機差異吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有不得不去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙控屍體？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳  想連我一起殺掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為射擊控制軟件的提升
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用高於你的精確度擊中針頭大小的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的腦前額葉什麼時候被燒燬的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經發出惡臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果是遙控屍體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼深的地底下要怎麼傳送電波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是利用那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個動作是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊都沒人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追久世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也追過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的武裝機甲是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸自沒有理由介入這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯伊爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齋籐先生去追了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那傢伙逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去追那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波瑪他們等一下會跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出港
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙好像下船去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去進行交易之後  他就不見人影了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的目的地是長崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救助巴特之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用傾斜旋翼機追
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特先生  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別管這個  少校人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝船出港去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用傾斜旋翼機追
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巴特放到塔奇克馬後面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯伊爾很久之前腦前額葉就被燒燬而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕俄國當局跟蹤柯伊爾之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就已經是遙控屍體了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈布羅夫與加賀崎都不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝機甲的駕駛員也是遙控屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概原本是佐川的人或工地的勞工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機甲也是陸自還沒驗收的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次交易有內幕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個應該可以成為調查久世資金支付來源的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像擁有令人難以置信的資金來源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面的追查以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先繞到色丹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有同型的偽裝船已經從出島出港了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等同伴到了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再穿過海保的監視網\N（海上保安廳）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在於剛剛那些人如果從空中追過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先準備好防空炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  被打敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追久世的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川  把那傢伙甩下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆嗎  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有追來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是他替我們擋下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易情報洩漏給當局了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是鈽已經到手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣出島就將成為我們的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能太樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到送進出島再說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始由我一個人前往出島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在色丹下船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前航行就會出現海上保安廳的巡邏艇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況不是還有走陸路這一招嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以欺騙警察的耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從陸地無法進入出島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進去只有從海上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況為了宣佈獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過海上保安廳的監視網\N把鈽帶進去的話比較有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立在公開展示之上的核武
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟只是一種嚇阻力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拿來使用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就更應該去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟海保戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一個人也能存活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會把鈽帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們在的話只會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都說得這麼直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能相信你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在300萬的難民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在同步注視著我的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能在這裡退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道警的直升機嗎\N（北海道警察）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直有種既視感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是也看過同樣的光景嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請優先處理巴特與石川的救助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有海上保安廳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很遺憾  不過還是麻煩你知會一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶帕茲與波瑪去調查佐川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是久世已經拿到鈽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海保就是最終防衛線了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出島已經做好數艘同型偽裝船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請他們要特別注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從距離上考量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他們要花幾天才會\N穿過公海出現在長崎外海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有照相館的預約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你得了健忘症嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是來往40年的上澤照相館\N那個繼承父業的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過度無人化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許僅僅靠特殊化的才能\N已經無法生活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去情報處理室和記憶管理室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去社長室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次交易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是內廳導演的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能沒把鈽交給久世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找出相關證據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然合田目標已經完成十之八九
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  他應該是打算製造\N難民已經先有核武的既成事實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來當作派遣自衛軍的決定性證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到東西就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去將會跟難民內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現政權擴軍的想法就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你打算如何解決不斷惡化的難民問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀崎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這邊看來是假義體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換到本體想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈布羅夫與他的部下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人化反而害了他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟克氯丹一樣被殺了也沒人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都被刪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克氯丹的資料就成了唯一的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕茲  波瑪  你們那邊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊只剩下跟公司有關的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有大量刪除資料的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很難復原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從相關狀況來判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次交易好像是在內廳的操控下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有內廳操縱柯伊爾的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄現場之後先回本部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解\N瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還是在合田掌握當中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒過個3天  身體還不習慣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老傢伙的傷勢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好腦部沒有發現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要一個月才能痊癒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次事件我們蒙受極大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊員的死亡  負傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連傾斜旋翼機都失去了\N可以說是徹底被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久世的偽裝船還沒出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海保的監視網還沒有逮到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府也沒有特別的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難民現在也很安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一致的見解是欠缺出動自衛軍的依據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是透過非正式管道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  中國政府一直很關切\N我國對自治區的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼自治區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明連難民都不肯收留
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話態度還這麼自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茅葺會被稱為親中派
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就是拿中國的發言當靠山的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在即使在海上保安廳內部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有一部分人知道\N偽裝船上可能載著鈽元素
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但神崎議員那邊卻已經透過獨自的管道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握到這次的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此應該認為在執政黨內部\N已經有不少人掌握到事情狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  高倉官房長官還是按兵不動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為他們認為\N只要鈽照內廳的劇本被帶進出島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會造成既成事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除派遣自衛軍的障礙\N所以覺得游刃有餘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在部分網路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對俄國黑手黨和難民之間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行過鈽元素交易的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始出現騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難民那邊要怎麼出牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果正如少校的判斷\N久世並沒有拿到鈽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為久世會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他用無與倫比的領袖魅力\N不尋常的行動力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及正確的情勢判斷\N將事態引導到目前這個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  他到底還是一名恐怖份子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管在戰略上或戰力上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有國家當後盾的合氏還是比他高明一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結果來看久世的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不偏離合田的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照他的想法扮演局勢演變的推手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際上他並不在合田控制之下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有能夠逆轉局勢的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的行動或許就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說起來有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Stand Alone Complex所造成的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有報告指出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上保安廳的巡邏艇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於長崎外海天草灘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現可能是久世搭乘的偽裝船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在傳送狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有來自巡邏艇的現場影像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接到這邊的螢幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光嚇阻沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船再靠過去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船再靠過去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備射擊船體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊船體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊船體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊船體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認命中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷  右舷中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正遭到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正當防衛射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火  開火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開燃料槽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把鈽炸飛了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個影像媒體也在播放喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船體好像起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕船員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船靠過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近一點把船攔下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長崎那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長崎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸熄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難民發動大停電恐怖活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了掩護久世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說很難想像難民能做到這個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在憎恨連鎖的盡頭等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將是與難民之間的泥沼戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個聲音\N醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字\N然後現出光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省視自身\N醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我\N時間已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去讓這一切成真的\N它就在裡面
